resources.description:
Send content to subscriber.

### Parameters
#### Body
- Data format: `https://manychat.github.io/dynamic_block_docs/`.
- Supported message tags: `https://developers.facebook.com/docs/messenger-platform/send-messages/message-tags#supported_tags`.
- More about message tags in ManyChat: `https://support.manychat.com/support/solutions/articles/36000195552-message-tags`.
> Attention! After January 15, 2020 requests without message tag may cause error

```json
{
  "subscriber_id": 0,
  "data": {
    "version": "v2",
    "content": {
      "messages": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Welcome to ManyChat Dynamic Response"
        }
      ],
      "actions": [],
      "quick_replies": []
    }
  },
  "message_tag": "ACCOUNT_UPDATE"
}
```

### Response
#### 200
```json
{
  "status": "success"
}
```

#### 400
```json
{
  "status": "error",
  "message": "string"
}
```

